comments: Hield (IND) makes contact with the ball after Beal's (PHX) gather and immediately slides it off as marginal contact occurs defending his driving shot attempt.
Beal's (PHX) slides over and makes marginal contact with Nembhard (IND) at the end of his drive.
Booker (PHX) extends his arms into Nesmith's (IND) body, which affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Hield (IND) places his forearm to Allen's (PHX) side while moving along his path to the basket and marginal body contact occurs contesting his driving shot attempt.
Hield (IND) is firming up and absorbs the marginal body contact as Booker (PHX) attempts to defend under the pick as they come together.
Nembhard (IND) brings his off-arm outward and marginal contact occurs with Allen (PHX) during the driving shot attempt.
Toppin (IND) stands on the lane line and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hield (IND) jumps alongside Beal's (PHX) path and lightly brushes Beal's arm defending his driving shot attempt.
Beal (PHX) moves into Nembhard's (IND) path and makes illegal body contact, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Siakam's (IND) arm after the release.

Replay review of the foul called on Booker (PHX) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Gordon (PHX) makes contact with the ball, dislodging it away from Siakam (IND) during rebounding. Booker (PHX) makes marginal contact with Siakam's arm after the ball becomes loose.
After the ball becomes loose, Siakam (IND) and Allen (PHX) engage and disengage with one another as marginal body contact occurs off ball.
Booker (PHX) hedges the pick and cleanly dislodges the ball away from Nembhard (IND) as they come together during his drive.
Allen (PHX) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Nembhard (IND) prior to incidental arm contact occurring during the drive.
Siakam (IND) commits a take foul on Durant (PHX).
Nembhard (IND) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Booker (PHX) contests the jump shot attempt by Nesmith (IND) and any contact with his non-shooting hand is marginal.
